&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;== sanity test 316: lfs mv =============================== 17:59:01 (1643047141)
lfs mv: /mnt/lustre/d316.sanity/d/file migrate failed: No such file or directory (2)
lfs mv: cannot migrate &apos;/mnt/lustre/d316.sanity/d&apos; to MDT0001: No such file or directory
